OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776906184
OL,3,C'Trumpflation' is here - and prices
OL,4,Care heading in the wrong direction
OL,6,FPrices across the United Kingdom rose
OL,7,Fat an annual rate of 3.3% in March - a
OL,8,Fleg up from 3% in February - as the
OL,9,Feconomic aftershock of war in Iran
OL,10,Fbegan to be felt.
OL,12,FHigher inflation was driven by the
OL,13,Fprice of heating oil and fuel.
OL,15,FPetrol rose by 8 pence a litre last
OL,16,Fmonth; diesel prices rose by 17 pence.
OL,17,FAnd it was just the beginning.
OL,19,FDomestic energy bills are set to rise
OL,20,Fin July and again in October - if the
OL,21,FStrait of Hormuz remains closed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
