OL,3,C'Trumpflation' is here - and prices
OL,4,Care heading in the wrong direction
OL,6,FFood and drink inflation has edged up
OL,7,Fto 3.7%.
OL,9,F"The clouds are gathering but the
OL,10,Fstorm has not yet broken," warns the
OL,11,FFood and Drink Federation (FDF).
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FWhen fossil fuel prices rise, food
OL,19,Fbecomes more expensive to grow,
OL,20,Ftransport, process, package, heat and
OL,21,Fchill.
