OL,3,C'Trumpflation' is here - and prices
OL,4,Care heading in the wrong direction
OL,6,FThe FDF has double-digit inflation
OL,7,Fpencilled in for Christmas - and
OL,8,Fthat's in its "best-case" scenario.
OL,10,FWe are in the foothills of something
OL,11,Fserious, but let's not scare ourselves
OL,12,Fsenseless.
OL,14,FNo economist believes the wave of
OL,15,Finflation now building is on anything
OL,16,Flike the scale of the one we lived
OL,17,Fthrough when Russia invaded Ukraine.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@YO]
