OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776906184
OL,3,C'Trumpflation' is here - and prices
OL,4,Care heading in the wrong direction
OL,6,F"Trumpflation" - as government
OL,7,Fofficials call it in private, but
OL,8,Fdefinitely not in public - looks less
OL,9,Fpainful.
OL,11,F"This is not our war," the chancellor
OL,12,Fsaid in a statement this morning -
OL,13,Fdistancing the government from the
OL,14,Fprice rises voters are now grappling
OL,15,Fwith, and reminding them that the
OL,16,Fprime minister resisted the clamour to
OL,17,Frush in behind US and Israeli attacks.
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@NO]sD@AOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
