PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776906184
OL,3,C'Trumpflation' is here - and prices
OL,4,Care heading in the wrong direction
OL,6,F"We've taken #117 off energy bills,
OL,7,Ffrozen rail fares and protected
OL,8,Fmotorists with the fuel duty freeze.
OL,9,FWe're acting to protect people from
OL,10,Funfair price rises, to bring down food
OL,11,Fprices at the till, and are boosting
OL,12,Flong-term energy security."
OL,14,FFair enough but a squeeze is coming.
OL,15,FVoters hate inflation and - fairly or
OL,16,Fnot - tend to blame the government of
OL,17,Fthe day.
OL,19,FMarkets expect the Bank of England to
OL,20,Fraise interest rates at least once
OL,21,Fbefore the year is out.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@[O]
