CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776906184
OL,3,C'Trumpflation' is here - and prices
OL,4,Care heading in the wrong direction
OL,6,FThat's not nailed on. Higher rates
OL,7,Fwon't restore the flow of oil, gas,
OL,8,Ffertiliser and jet fuel from the
OL,9,FMiddle East.
OL,11,FThey would, however, hit households
OL,12,Fand businesses if they respond to
OL,13,Fanother squeeze on living standards by
OL,14,Fdemanding higher pay or raising prices
OL,15,F- increasing upward pressure on
OL,16,Finflation.
OL,18,FWe're not there yet and may never be.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
