PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776906184
OL,3,C'Trumpflation' is here - and prices
OL,4,Care heading in the wrong direction
OL,6,FThe economy is weak and inflation is
OL,7,Fgathering pace. Both are bad; it is
OL,8,Fnot yet clear which is worse.
OL,10,F"We still think a prolonged pause,
OL,11,Frather than a series of interest rate
OL,12,Fhikes, is the most likely outcome,"
OL,13,Fsaid Capital Economics.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
